M||tx|---
M||titl|Dependency-Based Parallelization
M||impa|ct
M||impa|2-10× improvement
M||tags|async, parallelization, dependencies, better-all
M||tx|---
M|Depe|tx|For operations w/ partial dependencies, use `better-all` to maximize parallelism. It automatically starts each task at the earliest possible moment.
M|Depe|**In|**
M|Depe|tx|```ts
M|Depe|tx|const [us, config] = await Promise.all([
M|Depe|tx|fetchUser(),
M|Depe|tx|fetchConfig()
M|Depe|tx|])
M|Depe|tx|const profile = await fetchProfile(us.id)
M|Depe|tx|```
M|Depe|**Co|**
M|Depe|tx|```ts
M|Depe|tx|import { all } from 'better-all'
M|Depe|tx|const { us, config, profile } = await all({
M|Depe|tx|async us() { return fetchUser() },
M|Depe|tx|async config() { return fetchConfig() },
M|Depe|tx|async profile() {
M|Depe|tx|return fetchProfile((await this.$.us).id)
M|Depe|tx|}
M|Depe|tx|})
M|Depe|tx|```
M|Depe|**Al|**
M|Depe|tx|We can also cr all the promises first, and do `Promise.all()` at the end.
M|Depe|tx|```ts
M|Depe|tx|const userPromise = fetchUser()
M|Depe|tx|const profilePromise = userPromise.then(us => fetchProfile(us.id))
M|Depe|tx|const [us, config, profile] = await Promise.all([
M|Depe|tx|userPromise,
M|Depe|tx|fetchConfig(),
M|Depe|tx|profilePromise
M|Depe|tx|])
M|Depe|tx|```
M|Depe|Refe|[https://github.com/shuding/better-all](https://github.com/shuding/better-all)